

Day-17 The Only SQL GROUP BY & HAVING Video You Need (Full 100 Minute Tutorial)
===================================================================================


IMP NOTE - If we are Using GROUP BY so in the Select Column we Can Only Add Aggregation Functions like (COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX) If we enter any other thing this will Throw an Error.


GROUP BY
=========

1) We have a Business Requirement that we want Total Sales Category Wise




A) So first we will have to Check How many Categories we have 

SELECT DISTINCT category FROM sales;


Output - 

+-------------+
| category    |
+-------------+
| Electronics |
| Furniture   |
| Clothing    |
| Toys        |
| Books       |
+-------------+






B) 

SELECT category, SUM(amount) AS total_sales
FROM sales
GROUP BY category;



Output - 

+-------------+-------------+
| category    | total_sales |
+-------------+-------------+
| Electronics |   987529.46 |
| Furniture   |   951827.20 |
| Clothing    |  1059654.78 |
| Toys        |   976272.50 |
| Books       |   987687.07 |
+-------------+-------------+








2) Count of Products in Each Category

SELECT category, COUNT(DISTINCT product) AS total_products FROM sales GROUP BY category;


Output - 

