4) 3 Products with Maximum Sales

SELECT product, SUM (quantity) AS total_quantity, 
FROM sales 
GROUP BY product 
ORDER BY total_quantity DESC 
LIMIT 3; 



Output - 

+---------+----------------+
| product | total_quantity |
+---------+----------------+
| Dress   |           2409 |
| Jeans   |           2385 |
| Shoes   |           2376 |
+---------+----------------+








5) We want Total Sales & Number of Transactions Per Store Location 

SELECT store_location, SUM(amount) AS total_sales, COUNT(*) AS total_num_of_transactions  
FROM sales
GROUP BY store_location;



